# Plan Workflow Trigger

When the user asks for an implementation plan, design spec, architecture document, or types `/plan`:

1. Follow the procedure in `.cursor/workflows/plan.md`.
2. Write the plan to a Markdown file and do not print full plan content in chat.
3. Open it in Review Mode using `open_review`.
4. Report a concise status update and wait for feedback.
5. When the user asks to iterate or says `/review`, run the review workflow trigger.
6. Never ask the user to paste Review Mode comments; fetch annotations directly.
